com.jibrok.jira.plugins.timeinstatus.api

Class TimerActionDto

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jibrok.jira.plugins.timeinstatus.api.TimerActionDto

  • public class TimerActionDto
extends java.lang.Object
    The class is used to pass parameters about the action with a timer. For example, you need to pause the timer - for this you need to specify which timer, on which task, whether after this a re-index is needed. All these parameters contain this class. It you can only create using constructors that will verify the correctness of the settings passed. * @see Example>
